2016-06-24 0.4.0 (Wim Bonthuis <wim@500k.nl>)
- Added verification of downloaded package with https://github.com/lwf/puppet-remote_file, included as new dependency.
- Download packages to archive directory, /var/cache/puppet/archives by default.
- Added beaker (albeit somewhat minimal) and puppet-rspec tests.
- Moved most parameters to params.pp.
- Added some new (configurable) parameters.
- Added ruby 2.4 to travis.
- Prepared init.pp for puppet4 and puppet strings.
- Initialized changelog.
- Updated README.
